lead_paragraph: It would be hard to bet against the Williams sisters meeting in their first Wimbledon final since 2009, but Angelique Kerber and Elena Vesnina won't just be making up the numbers in the last four on Thursday.

headline.print_headline: Kerber and Vesnina Out to Halt March of Williams Sisters
